quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,“Hâ-Mîm
  44,2,“Ndikulumbilira buku lofotokoza momveka
  44,3,“Ndithu tidaivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wodala. Ife ndithu Ndiachenjezi
  44,4,“Mu (usiku) umenewu chinthu chilichonse chanzeru chimaweruzidwa ndi kulongosoledwa
  44,5,“Mwa chilamulo chochokera kwa Ife. Ndithu Ife ndife otumiza atumiki (kuti achenjeze anthu)
  44,6,"“(Chifukwa cha) chifundo chochokera kwa Mbuye wako. Ndithu Iye Ngwakumva zonse, Wodziwa kwabasi"
  44,7,"“Mbuye wa thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake, ngati muli otsimikiza"
  44,8,"“Palibe wopembedzedwa moona koma Iye basi. Amapereka moyo ndikupereka imfa, Mbuye wanu ndi Mbuye wa makolo anu oyamba"
  44,9,"“Koma iwo (okanira) ali mchikaiko akungosewera, (potsatira zilakolako zawo zoipa)"
  44,10,"“Basi, yembekezera tsiku limene thambo lidzadze ndi utsi woonekera (konsekonse)"
  44,11,"“Udzawaphimba anthu onse (ndipo adzakhala akunena:) “Ichi ndi chilango chowawa"
  44,12,"“E Mbuye wathu! Tichotsereni chilangochi, ndithu ife tikhulupirira.”"
  44,13,“(Kodi lero) kukumbukira kuwapindulira chiyani iwo? Chikhalirecho mtumiki wolongosola chilichonse adawadzera
  44,14,"“Koma sadamlabadire uku akumnena kuti: “Waphunzitsidwa (ndi anthu), ndiponso wopenga.”"
  44,15,“Ndithu Ife tichotsa chilangocho pang’ono (koma) inu mubwerezanso (machimo anu)
  44,16,"“(Kumbuka, iwe Mtumiki), tsiku limene tidzawalanga chilango chachikulu; ndithu Ife ndife olanga"
  44,17,"“Ndipo ndithu iwo asadadze, tidawayesa anthu a Farawo. Ndiponso adawadzera mtumiki wolemekezeka"
  44,18,"“Kuti: “Ndipatseni akapolo a Allah. Ndithu ine kwa inu ndi Mtumiki wokhulupirika.”"
  44,19,““Ndipo musadzikweze kwa Allah. Ndithu ine ndikubweretserani chisonyezo choonekera.”
  44,20,““Ndipo Ine ndadzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye Wanga ndiponso Mbuye wanu (ku chiwembu chofuna kundipha) pondigenda (ndi miyala).”
  44,21,"““Ndipo ngati simundikhulupirira, ndipatukeni (musandivutitse).”"
  44,22,"““(Koma adamchitira mtopola). Ndipo iye adaitana Mbuye wake kuti: “Awa ndithu ndi anthu oipa.”"
  44,23,"“(Allah adamuuza kuti): “Pita ndi akapolo Anga usiku; ndithu inu mulondoledwa.”"
  44,24,"““Ndipo isiye nyanja ili momwemo, zii. ndithu iwo ndikhamu (lankhondo) limene limizidwa.”"
  44,25,“Kodi ndi minda ingati ndi akasupe zomwe adazisiya atamizidwa
  44,26,“Ndiponso mmera ndi malo abwino
  44,27,“Ndi mtendere (waukulu) umene adali kusangalala nawo mmenemo
  44,28,“Umo ndi mmene zidalili. Ndipo tidawapatsa anthu ena zimenezo
  44,29,“Thambo ndi nthaka sizidawalilire ndipo sadapatsidwe mpata (wobwereranso pa dziko)